Class RMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openscience.cdk.isomorphism.mcss.RMap

  • public class RMap
extends Object
    An RMap implements the association between an edge (bond) in G1 and an edge (bond) in G2, G1 and G2 being the compared graphs in a RGraph context.
